title: Roger Goodell: Seahawks weren't fined, will be sold

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: Roger Goodell: Seahawks weren't fined, will be sold
sources.description: With the Seahawks in the Super Bowl and with reports recently emerging that the team will be sold by Paul Allen's sister, Jody — and that the team has been fined $5 million for non-compliance with NFL ownership requirements — the subject became low-hanging fruit for a question during Commissioner Roger Goodell's Super Bowl press conference.
